november 16 2006
	

within the application of a label...

Last night i felt a tremendous sucess as we managed to rekindle what initially caused a handful of people to join together and create a movement(however small it was)and bring a piece of it back for a moment in closing this chapter formally, rather than letting it fade away as seemed the likely case. i almost immediately came to tears when amidst a group hug someone said,"why can't we just be young again?".there's not one moment in the company of those kids that could be brought up in which i would not instantly have a mental photograph of the entire sequence played out. i remember it all.

This is the youth i tried so hard to consciously catch stride with and felt that i was too late. A couple bands in a basement with a few friends seems trivial in the grand scheme of one's life but in retrospective, it was the be all end all of my existence. these friendships truly moved me. the songs are still endless inspiration. Signs will flash now and again in the thick of the present tense, hinting at how special a moment is but rarely the chance for an overhead view is granted. if something feels so right, document it, love it, and live it.

In no way am i writing a eulogy for my/our youth. if anything i feel more in tune with it because of the past few weeks leading up to last night. all of the passion i felt over those will be enough to keep me in stride with my youth for the rest of my life.

 i am past/present/future proud of of us all, what we've done and what's to come.

Wednesday, December 20, 2006
	

like steak knives? like ducks?

at the height of consistency i fell asleep in a drainage ditch and came to terms with all oil based products. flying south for the winter (which happens to encompass the sacred bro holiday known as spring break) i lost all consciousness from december to spring. i awoke on a beach with three things we all wished for in a desert.

what have i lost, what can i find again, does found object have relevance to life as i know living without it. i am being too lineal. inactive physically, but the theory/thought patterns reoccur if only as a basis to construct new space in which creation/destruction takes place. should my cumulative life be taken into account when determining the now? yes and no. can you now smile upon your bits and pieces in aging euphoria? bitter bitter rainbows.some of these presently physical and in theory are still accessible, even though i feel the current relevance of them has tapered off. what exactly is killed off when life's light is redirected? physical? formulaic? historical? influence? surely not denial. these blasts are the keys to the non-lineal life living, and only in rare occurrences blow doors of their hinges. closure is not a collective process.

NO FUTURE FEST III

No Future Fest is one of the best chances you, the wasted noise junkie, has to see your favorite
acts in an intimate setting within a small friendly Southern city. Chapel Hill is located just six hours North of 
Atlanta, and five hours South of DC. During the day there are several museums, restaurants, parks, rope swings,
and other Carolina type shit within a short drive or a long walk. Day one is April 20th, doors at 7, show 
at 8. Day two is of course April 21st, doors at 3, free pizza from 3 - 4:30 for all, show starts at five.

a man sat and said something,
later, he wrote it down and died.
i read it, traveled to sit where he once sat,
thought about it staring into 
a face across from me in the city where this man's friends
declared a permanent feeling of love and romance, 
condemning architectural masculinity
leading me to believe that this moment will be the point 
in which a dichotomy is struck between my life up to said point 
and the rest of my life running over into oblivion.
i came home to live like days before,

how many corners can one room have? i've lost count but can still recall that i've left them all with an awkward feeling, each one exceeding that which the present was preceded by. as a collective, this entire room(right angles and all) is terribly detrimental to my already depleting posture.

sporadic fits of bliss.as posh as xenon.we all lust for light.thieves find light irresistible.im slashed from ear to ear.the gash is something to get lost in.regardless if you smoke.i have been pacing away the past few days.can you blame me?even in this physical world.the dichotomy still exists.mind and body(cognitive thinking and emotion).a specific vehicle and the operator of that specific vehicle which has been brought to our attention.their both pointing fingers.which faculty is responsible for this feeling?a feeling so small to start.its been days.growth.now im covered in it.the worst feeling ive ever known.i beg no questions.i just want you to know its there.and im doing everything i can to get rid of it.

they are a linear interpritation of formers- 20/16 vision graphed in a park setting-trees running y high and the sidewalk winds with the formers gaining ground titles wilting and fueling life's infancy- equating a perplexed scalp dry from fingers raking falls season away- rain a velocity my x can't bear a steady accumulation-collapsing with care-the precision of mother nature smears dirt to my face- this is not the same tree we fell from-apples einstein et al.

woke up the outlook different covered in birth from the first time i bore through your legs- a ride soon forgotten wearing like friction silk if you would-greatly insert i'd like to appreciate process this again coarse thighs remember a difficult face tense work i around in houses shared eight legs lust out of habit- the feel good minute of honesty is honestly anything sans make-up.

what's my take on it?
what do i have to say?

historically electrocuted reciprocal smiles
french in the future pits my stomach

there is a light release i've yet to find- the beauty shines-at the brink of panic panic panic- a glance is almost unbearable- beauty is an entity i wish to consume on my own- i wander through the moment through the limbs of my friends- my legs are cramps- beauty is to be shared vicariously if the necessary means are there- i'm glaring for emotion for a pinnacle for the city my eyes will feel and feast.

the existence of every facet- leading me up to this point is seemingly insurmountable- the night and people drive-movement-i am in midst of spiritual existence.
